{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "마이페이지 프로필 - View 모드 (시안 기반 레이아웃)"
  },
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "blur_until_loaded": {
    "enabled": true,
    "data_sources": "user"
  },
  "props": {
    "className": "space-y-6"
  },
  "responsive": {
    "portable": {
      "props": {
        "className": "space-y-4"
      }
    }
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "상태별 안내 메시지 - 비활성화 (회색 - secondary)",
      "if": "{{user.data?.status === 'inactive'}}",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": {
            "name": "circle-pause",
            "size": "lg",
            "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "P",
          "props": {
            "className": "text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          },
          "text": "$t:mypage.profile.status_inactive_notice"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "상태별 안내 메시지 - 차단 (빨간색 경고)",
      "if": "{{user.data?.status === 'blocked'}}",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": {
            "name": "ban",
            "size": "lg",
            "className": "text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 flex-shrink-0"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "P",
          "props": {
            "className": "text-sm text-red-800 dark:text-red-200"
          },
          "text": "$t:mypage.profile.status_blocked_notice"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "상태별 안내 메시지 - 탈퇴 (노란색 - warning)",
      "if": "{{user.data?.status === 'withdrawn'}}",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-800 rounded-lg"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": {
            "name": "circle-xmark",
            "size": "lg",
            "className": "text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 flex-shrink-0"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "flex flex-col gap-1"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "P",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-sm text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200"
              },
              "text": "$t:mypage.profile.status_withdrawn_notice"
            },
            {
              "if": "{{user.data?.withdrawn_at}}",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "P",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-xs text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-300"
              },
              "text": "$t:mypage.profile.withdrawn_at: {{user.data?.withdrawn_at}}"
